text: Wonderful collection of themes and paintings across void decks outdoor spaces, and building walls. Enjoy a stroll, feel the breeze, sit on the benches and absorb art surroundings. I especially appreciated the Van Gogh area with descriptions and dates offering additional context to the art.

Surprising find. Not common at all to have artwork at the void decks of hdbs so interesting. There's also artwork in the surrounding blocks but this has Van Gogh's artwork and stories about his art and his life. Interesting....ps from an australian tourist
That's a very good idea to bring art into community.
